    "body": "To attempt to clarify the use-case:\r\n\r\n* I download the state snapshot from somewhere\r\n* There is a tool that runs for half a year or whatever it takes, that results in true of false for whether the snapshot is valid.\r\n* This tool can run independent of p2p or network activity, and future states.\r\n\r\nSo In the end I guess it is a question of:\r\n\r\n* can I download such a snapshot independently in a sensible format\r\n* is there a tool that can perform the verification on such a snapshot",
